Carl has never been very interested in alcohol but has just
recently developed a love for whiskey. He wants to learn more and try
new whiskeys. He had his first Old Fashion while exploring the bar
scene in Austin and wants to learn how to recreate it at home.
Recipes tend to be difficult to follow and he never retains
the information so he can recreate recipes in the future.
Leanna enjoys making specialty cocktails at home,
but always makes the same thing. Ever since the pandemic
began, she misses going to happy hours with her
coworkers. Leanna wants to learn how to make some
specialty cocktails for Friday night happy hours after work.
Leanna has never tried meal-kit subscription
services due to cost. She has yet to find a service at the
right price point to make her want to commit.
